    "Within the context of current business practices, integrating technology and marketing has initiated a period of remarkable transformation (Kamkankaew et al., 2022).",
    "Artificial intelligence (AI) is a highly significant technological advancement that profoundly influences contemporary marketing (Ghodeswar & Krishna, 2022).",
